Package edu.umb.cs682.ecom.backend.payload.response

Class PreOrderResponse

  • Object
    • PreOrderResponse
  • public class PreOrderResponse
extends Object
    PreOrderResponse represents a response to the frontend with PreOrder details that the User must confirm before placing their order.

        Constructs a new PreOrderResponse object with the given details.
        Parameters:
        username - the username of the User that will place the order
        preOrder - the ID of the PreOrder generated for the user
        cart - the shopping cart details for the PreOrder
        products - the list of Products in the PreOrder
        taxes - the list of taxes in the PreOrder
        shipping - the list of shipping charges in the PreOrder
        itemCount - the total item count in the PreOrder
        subtotal - the subtotal of the PreOrder
        shippingCost - the total shipping cost of the PreOrder
        taxCost - the total taxes of the PreOrder
        total - the grand total price of the PreOrder
